{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ff79910bdb","title":"在十五省市委书记会议上的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"af7af2e717","index":0,"year":1955,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"ff79910bdb","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui3","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1949-1957卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui3a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"408173da57","type":"title","text":"在十五省市委书记会议上的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3e45122833","type":"paragraph","text":"民主人士下乡，提出粮食和镇反问题。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2b66ef7e4f","type":"paragraph","text":"必须依靠贫农，团结中农，合作社必须互利才能自愿，没有互利就不能自愿。牲口不归公，假公道，投资平摊，贫农给。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5f4a5428cc","type":"paragraph","text":"停、缩、发。该停者停，该发者发，该缩者缩。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c030b5e63a","type":"paragraph","text":"民主人士下乡考察，口径对一对，十几个省问题较多，他们提出来，我们抓住。","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8efd8e7ef3","type":"paragraph","text":"成绩、缺点，他们只讲成绩，不讲缺点。其实乱子不少，大体还好。看一下，好的、坏的、中等的，加以分析，清一清，多少没有乱子的。","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ddeedfb3f2","type":"paragraph","text":"反动势力猖獗，要讲一下。民主人士眼里没有反革命，借他们压一下有好处。","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b67ebdea05","type":"paragraph","text":"他们当民主人士也不好做，上不着天，下不着地。","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0775e94878","type":"paragraph","text":"合作社也乱子不少，大体还好。一日停，二日缩，三日发。缩，全缩半缩，少缩多缩，按实际情况。不干不行。","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"782dc6bd05","type":"paragraph","text":"后解放区，一般就是发，基本是发。华北、东北也要有发。","index":9,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"94e1203ca4","type":"paragraph","text":"该发即发，该停即停，该缩即缩。","index":10,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"79362336fd","type":"paragraph","text":"自愿互利，互利换得自愿。取得中农入社，即有利于贫农。半，半有利，不能解释为中农吃亏。从马列都没有说过这种话。贫农给贷款，腰杆硬起来。","index":11,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"33e6a32af4","type":"paragraph","text":"章程要完全不使中农吃亏。","index":12,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"de3ac3f350","type":"paragraph","text":"反革命五年抓一百五十万，每年三十万，少杀，关改多。我主多抓，民主人士主大赦，不便反对。宪法有，可以讨论。赦好？抓好？我已大赦过，党团三反都赦了，战犯也赦了不少，也有赦了又作反革命。","index":13,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9ef0717294","type":"paragraph","text":"手上还有一批，上校以上七百多，讲放不放，要张治中立状子，放出去能钓鱼。","index":14,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c26f2a24d0","type":"paragraph","text":"大捉特捉是重点，大赦特赦不是重点，是人民的意见。七月开会时，大家都认为有大捉必要。","index":15,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bcb8915c67","type":"paragraph","text":"粮食问题，党内外有潮流，曰：大事不好。我说：大事还好，有点乱子。五年计划，要搞粮食、搞供销。","index":16,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d992c48e33","type":"paragraph","text":"农民中缺粮户要粮，余粮户也要粮。从生产上解决。过剩粮不可买，空下来。","index":17,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c1d1a32aff","type":"paragraph","text":"主要矛盾：个体与国家，社会主义的矛盾。","index":18,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"618989f63c","type":"paragraph","text":"粮食工作五利：一利缺粮户，二利市民，三利灾民，四利城工，五利打台湾。","index":19,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e5f9853056","type":"paragraph","text":"粮食工作无损自给户，稍损余粮户。","index":20,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9f99ac0b57","type":"paragraph","text":"现在供应三亿人。","index":21,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f1bf2cb59d","type":"paragraph","text":"河南材料，缺粮户百分之一点五，该叫。","index":22,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6e081e7518","type":"paragraph","text":"统购问题，有人说定产高了，是偏低，是偏高？偏高多少？高有无百分之二十？弄清楚才能答复党内外的人。会议上插话（广西省汇报时）：","index":23,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"406051d557","type":"paragraph","text":"一万七千个社缩一、二百，小事。发展五千个社，少吧！","index":24,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3d2bf13f59","type":"paragraph","text":"（湖南省汇报时）：","index":25,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"66633f7cf3","type":"paragraph","text":"怪不得湖南不叫。（指粮食工作）","index":26,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"98d30b7113","type":"paragraph","text":"发展四千个，这么少，不到一翻呀！","index":27,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6a01da12d5","type":"paragraph","text":"（江西省汇报时）：","index":28,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c17edd85eb","type":"paragraph","text":"发展八千个，百分之三十四的乡。再发展一万四千个。","index":29,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"11e8887cbe","type":"paragraph","text":"（湖北省汇报时）：","index":30,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"779e822255","type":"paragraph","text":"周转粮不能没有，不放入计划，好呀！不买过头粮，不计周转粮。","index":31,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6ced04e3c2","type":"paragraph","text":"（浙江省汇报时）：","index":32,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e83c58b006","type":"paragraph","text":"现在五万五千个，已退七千个，再退三千个，尚余四万五千，空白乡还要发展，其余各省可否翻一翻。","index":33,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9e5c8fbfb2","type":"paragraph","text":"（江苏省汇报时）：","index":34,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0a24aca624","type":"paragraph","text":"落后乡百分之五有反革命，百分之十坏人，蜕化分子，这是反革命同盟军，县区乡三级干部要调查。不能让中农作主，中农可以教育，他要按党的政策办事也可以。","index":35,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c04a8995c7","type":"paragraph","text":"三万二千个不发展？！要比一比浙江。","index":36,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"739253f603","type":"paragraph","text":"（安徽省汇报时）：","index":37,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1cfdc359f1","type":"paragraph","text":"不发达的省，要利用发达省的经验。江苏赶上去，湘鄂两广要放手发展。合作社多数要大发展，百分之九十较好，百分之十退。","index":38,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d9234d43d9","type":"paragraph","text":"（山东省汇报时）：","index":39,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cd9fd0d6e8","type":"paragraph","text":"死人真省粮？湖南说死几十人，只死一人。现象、本质分开，一股台风天黑了，不得了。一查，是假的，合作社百分之九十是好的，是经多次风的。再讲几点：","index":40,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"db5d02ad9f","type":"paragraph","text":"一、证明百分之三至五，机动幅度再研究，不决定。八百八十亿，十一亿重点减。湖南、安徽、山东要加一点。交粮食会议，为粮食需要者设。","index":41,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6be1567cdf","type":"paragraph","text":"二、层层负责有好处，但会形成无数独立王国。二十多万个要统一、分级。统一计划下各省负责。","index":42,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5e6e558665","type":"paragraph","text":"三、周转粮、细粮、粗粮照旧。不要在粮食上舞弊，供应太广。××缺是假缺。","index":43,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9fac2770fc","type":"paragraph","text":"四、合作社自愿互利，如果自愿，要拍扳。承认了的，照着办，保证百分之九十可靠。","index":44,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c02131054e","type":"paragraph","text":"五、习、法、公核有争执，党委统一，合法又敏觉，做好。饶、潘、杨案子，包庇三个反革命。用大叛徒胡京和。可以传达到十四级以上。","index":45,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f4958fd52a","type":"paragraph","text":"胡风案子另发通知，那个字号不清楚。","index":46,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"ff79910bdb","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":137,"end":134}}}},"__N_SSG":true}